OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784029691
OL,3,CALN funding row throws Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's budget plans into jeopardy
OL,6,FThe dispute means that, as things
OL,7,Fstand, the Welsh Government is set to
OL,8,Flose the vote on its spending plans in
OL,9,Fthe Senedd next Tuesday.
OL,11,FTalks began after the Plaid Cymru
OL,12,FWelsh Government published its plans
OL,13,Fin its Supplementary Budget, which
OL,14,Fisn't a full budget but rather sets
OL,15,Fout some adjustments in the current
OL,16,Ffinancial year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
