PN,43903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784029691
OL,3,CALN funding row throws Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's budget plans into jeopardy
OL,6,FIt maintains the overall spending
OL,7,Fplans of the previous Labour Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment but adds #145m towards
OL,9,Fcutting waiting lists in hospitals
OL,10,Falong with #55m towards childcare
OL,11,Ffunding and spending on school
OL,12,Fmaintenance and other capital projects.
OL,14,FPlaid Cymru was the largest party
OL,15,Fafter May's Senedd Election so forms
OL,16,Fthe Welsh Government, but it doesn't
OL,17,Fhave a majority so needs the support
OL,18,Fof another party in order to win votes.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
