PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784029691
OL,3,CALN funding row throws Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's budget plans into jeopardy
OL,6,FAs a result of spending in England
OL,7,Frelated to ALN, the Welsh Government
OL,8,Freceived a #327m boost to its budget
OL,9,Ffor this financial year.
OL,11,FIt's not required to spend that money
OL,12,Fin the same areas and the current
OL,13,FPlaid Cymru and previous Labour Welsh
OL,14,FGovernments argued that it didn't all
OL,15,Fneed to be spent on ALN because Wales
OL,16,Ffaces different needs in that sector.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
