PN,43906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784029691
OL,3,CALN funding row throws Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's budget plans into jeopardy
OL,6,FHowever those speaking for schools and
OL,7,Flocal authorities, along with trade
OL,8,Funions, say that spending on ALN is
OL,9,Ftaking up increasing amounts of
OL,10,Fresources.
OL,12,FTalks, which have been going on all
OL,13,Fweek, between the Welsh Government and
OL,14,Fthe Labour group seem to have hit an
OL,15,Fimpasse.
OL,17,FPlaid Cymru has accused Labour of
OL,18,F"walking away from an offer of #80m of
OL,19,Fextra funding for Additional Learning
OL,20,FNeeds".
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
