PN,43907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784029691
OL,3,CALN funding row throws Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's budget plans into jeopardy
OL,6,FThe party says that it made the offer,
OL,7,Fwhich would be "evenly split between
OL,8,Fthe current financial year and next",
OL,9,Fbut that that offer was rejected.
OL,11,FPlaid Cymru MS Keira Marshall was
OL,12,Fquoted as saying: "It is deeply
OL,13,Firresponsible for Labour to walk away
OL,14,Ffrom such a constructive offer of #80m
OL,15,Ftowards ALN by our Plaid Cymru
OL,16,FGovernment."
OL,26,@oD@POUpD@dO]tD@SOUxD@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
