PN,43908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784029691
OL,3,CALN funding row throws Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's budget plans into jeopardy
OL,6,FShe added that: "Parents, pupils and
OL,7,Fteachers will rightly question
OL,8,FLabour's commitment to this issue now
OL,9,Fthat they have chosen to reject what
OL,10,Fwould have been a very positive step
OL,11,Fforward for those campaigning on this
OL,12,Fissue."
OL,14,FHowever Labour disputes the claim that
OL,15,Fit has walked away from talks.
OL,26,@nD@QOUtD@GO]
