PN,43910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784029691
OL,3,CALN funding row throws Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's budget plans into jeopardy
OL,6,FHe goes on to say: "The latest
OL,7,Fsuggested quantum of investment for
OL,8,Fadditional learning needs discussed
OL,9,Fbetween our parties continues to fall
OL,10,Fshort of this mark. As already
OL,11,Fmentioned, I recognise there has been
OL,12,Fprogress and movement in recent days.
OL,13,FIn that same spirit, I would urge the
OL,14,FGovernment to continue that movement
OL,15,Fand make at least #100 million
OL,16,Favailable for investment in ALN so
OL,17,Fthat we can then help deliver a
OL,18,Fpositive supplementary budget for
OL,19,FWales."
OL,26,@nD@TOU{D@GO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
