PN,43911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784029691
OL,3,CALN funding row throws Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's budget plans into jeopardy
OL,6,FA Welsh Labour Spokesperson added:
OL,7,F"There wasn't a penny on the table for
OL,8,Fadditional learning needs until Welsh
OL,9,FLabour fought for it.
OL,11,F"#40million this year falls far short
OL,12,Fof what children and young people with
OL,13,Fadditional learning needs require.
OL,15,F"Schools, teaching unions and councils
OL,16,Fare clear in their support for our
OL,17,Fposition. We will not back down.
OL,19,F"This is about getting the best
OL,20,Fpossible deal for vulnerable children
OL,21,Fand young people."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
