PN,43912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784029691
OL,3,CALN funding row throws Welsh
OL,4,CGovernment's budget plans into jeopardy
OL,6,FIf no deal can be reached before
OL,7,FTuesday, it seems certain that the
OL,8,FWelsh Government will lose the vote.
OL,9,FAs it's not a full budget, it's
OL,10,Funlikely to bring down the government,
OL,11,Fbut it will prove an embarrassment and
OL,12,Fcause a headache.
OL,14,FIt will mean the Finance Minister will
OL,15,Fhave to draw up a new set of proposals
OL,16,Fand bring a new supplementary budget
OL,17,Fto the Senedd in the autumn.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/13
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
